{"tid":2325110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新巴技工確診 曾參加教會聚會有確診個案","createTime":"2020-12-14T11:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T14:55:09.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9669accee622ab9ecdd0d775309eddc37912b1ca","tid":2325110,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:54:31.000Z","msg":"新巴柴灣創富道車廠1名巴士技工，確診感染新型冠狀病毒。 新巴表示，今日收到這名員工的家人通知，他昨晚確診，上星期六最後一日上班，他早前參加的教會聚會有確診個案。新巴指，已安排曾經一同共事的24名員工接受病毒檢測，並徹底消毒清潔相關的工作間、巴士、員工食堂及更衣室 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港版新天地教"},{"pid":"937681c5fcc1ca3c695bd7413338bd7a78ead6dd","tid":2325110,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"乘機禁基督教伊斯蘭教"},{"pid":"0ae108c8cfd6db370ce113853635eb2d7c116fbd","tid":2325110,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab36f68daef759d458b7431975633f94faa20af","tid":2325110,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T14:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}